RSAWEB has partnered with MyBroadband to provide insight into the Cloud. Ask your questions about the Cloud, and Sean Rose, RSAWEB’s Cloud Product Manager, will answer them. Post your questions in the RSAWEB forum thread here. By asking your questions you will not only get insight into the Cloud, but also stand a chance to win cool prizes. For business use cases, Sean can also provide excellent insight into the 5 stages of successful Cloud Data Management: Backup, Visibility, Activation, Orchestration, and Automation. Here are the rules for the discussion: Please post your questions in this thread, and Sean will start to answer your questions from 12:00 on Thursday (25 July). The best 3 questions, as selected by Sean, will each win an Amazon Echo Dot.